Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.24,0:02:42.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魯路修
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.95,0:02:46.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對 我就是ZERO
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.00,0:02:57.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ZERO
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.69,0:02:59.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是魯路修
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.98,0:03:02.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他利用了日本人和你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.74,0:03:05.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要保護這種人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.39,0:03:18.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ZERO 我要結果了你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.10,0:03:24.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我敗給了過去的自己 敗給了朱雀
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.56,0:03:28.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,並且被他
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.55,0:03:31.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,押送到布里塔尼亞皇帝面前
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.42,0:03:42.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前第17皇位繼承人 魯路修·V·布里塔尼亞
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.25,0:03:45.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久違了 吾兒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.72,0:03:47.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這混帳…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.16,0:03:49.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別想使用Geass
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.27,0:03:55.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請恕我直言 陛下
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.54,0:03:58.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請讓本人加入帝國最強十二騎士
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.45,0:04:00.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,圓桌騎士（Knight Of Rounds）
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.90,0:04:04.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是在要求抓住ZERO的獎勵？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.05,0:04:06.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.24,0:04:07.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說過 魯路修
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.30,0:04:11.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要從內部改變這個世界
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.59,0:04:13.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,踏著友人的屍體往上爬嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.68,0:04:14.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.09,0:04:17.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.52,0:04:19.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才的回答甚合朕意
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.76,0:04:24.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 朕命令圓桌騎士
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.61,0:04:26.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遮住ZERO的左眼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.91,0:04:28.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,YES Your Majesty
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.24,0:04:34.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身為皇子卻揭竿而起的不肖兒
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.60,0:04:37.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但你還有利用價值
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.76,0:04:39.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.74,0:04:42.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,篡改你的記憶
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.17,0:04:45.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身為ZERO的事 瑪莉安娜的事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.29,0:04:47.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以及娜娜莉的事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.77,0:04:49.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道是…Geass
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.84,0:04:53.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忘卻一切做個凡人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.77,0:04:54.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.85,0:04:57.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你又想奪走嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.10,0:04:59.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,母親 甚至娜娜莉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.82,0:05:03.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,查爾斯·D·布里塔尼亞給予刻印
