Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.89,0:05:46.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找出賦予皇帝Geass能力的人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.81,0:05:47.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有娜娜莉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.50,0:05:53.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有妹妹 卻沒有弟弟
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.98,0:05:55.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.97,0:05:59.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了 是布里塔尼亞軍吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.19,0:06:01.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在找我哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.15,0:06:05.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有這棟樓的構造圖
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.06,0:06:07.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卻沒有識別號碼的記錄
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.59,0:06:09.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這Knightmare還是不能用嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.71,0:06:11.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那邊的在幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.54,0:06:14.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看服裝是學生吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.22,0:06:17.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是軍人嗎 得救了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.35,0:06:19.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快處理他的傷勢吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.85,0:06:23.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,機密情報局的人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.56,0:06:25.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,皇帝陛下的直屬部隊怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.15,0:06:28.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 情報無誤
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.89,0:06:31.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡拉雷斯的軍隊不知道我的事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.25,0:06:33.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以利用 這個數據
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.44,0:06:35.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有一個倖存者嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.80,0:06:36.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.18,0:06:38.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.32,0:06:39.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.25,0:06:40.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.50,0:06:44.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我吧 你的Knightmare
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.62,0:06:55.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.22,0:07:00.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,識別號碼是QR5-YK1D6
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.19,0:07:02.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.04,0:07:07.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖說發動Geass必須直視對方的眼睛…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.17,0:07:10.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不老不死的魔女可沒資格說我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.73,0:07:15.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還在反擊？恐怖分子？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.48,0:07:15.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.50,0:07:19.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,似乎已俘獲我軍的Knightmare
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.71,0:07:20.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真丟人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.94,0:07:22.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但敵方是弱勢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.04,0:07:24.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可否讓我去…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.04,0:07:28.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 你只是暫居於此的客座將士
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.29,0:07:32.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡該由我這個總督去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.00,0:07:32.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.33,0:07:38.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中華料理的調料不合我口味
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.23,0:07:40.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且很有趣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.59,0:07:42.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,狩獵人類
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.60,0:07:52.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,粉身碎骨吧 布里塔尼亞
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.56,0:08:03.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幹得好 Q1
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.14,0:08:05.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來去21層
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.19,0:08:07.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,P4封鎖樓梯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.89,0:08:11.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,R5左轉30度
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.60,0:08:18.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,N1 從那裡向50米處天花板齊射
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.85,0:08:27.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24}埃米利卿 通信斷絕
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.41,0:08:29.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24}IFF（敵我識別裝置）代碼變更
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.15,0:08:30.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24}這是第5次了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.65,0:08:31.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24}歐提斯隊 全滅
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.18,0:08:34.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能 到底是誰在指揮恐怖分子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.01,0:08:36.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.49,0:08:37.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總督
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.31,0:08:42.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ZERO的真面目居然是學生
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.86,0:08:45.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過 氣度到底是不同
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.10,0:08:49.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,步兵部隊 ZERO搶到的Sutherland還有剩餘
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.69,0:08:50.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快上去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.33,0:08:52.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有ZERO在就能贏
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.90,0:08:55.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇跡會發生 會發生的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.89,0:08:57.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這恐怖分子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.59,0:09:04.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差不多該卡拉雷斯總督登場了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.43,0:09:05.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來很順利
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.37,0:09:08.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡蓮 你不是去21層了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.38,0:09:10.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想留在你身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.59,0:09:15.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終於能兩人獨處了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.26,0:09:23.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,11區的餌好像引人上鉤了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.93,0:09:25.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是C.C.嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.47,0:09:27.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還不清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.08,0:09:29.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,樞木
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.27,0:09:33.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是第一個進來這裡的圓桌騎士
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.11,0:09:36.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連修奈澤爾他們也不知道這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.64,0:09:38.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甚感榮幸 陛下
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.51,0:09:40.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但為何讓本人…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.54,0:09:44.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,圓桌騎士中只有你知道
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.64,0:09:49.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ZERO的真面目和Geass
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.00,0:09:54.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡是…神殿？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.79,0:09:58.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 這裡是…對了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.50,0:10:01.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毀滅神的武器
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.42,0:10:02.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,武器？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.43,0:10:05.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名為阿克夏（Akashic）之劍
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.91,0:10:14.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在神根島對ZERO見死不救的你 有什麼話要說
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.19,0:10:18.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魯路修 你一直在騙我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.34,0:10:22.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是說ZERO本是你同班同學
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.30,0:10:24.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是說Geass的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.28,0:10:26.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兩者都是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.58,0:10:31.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回答我 你對我也用過Geass嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.49,0:10:34.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,扭曲我的心靈 讓我服從你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.83,0:10:36.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魯路修
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.81,0:10:39.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的心屬於你自己
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.12,0:10:41.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對ZERO的忠誠和仰慕都是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.72,0:10:42.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不許動
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.02,0:10:45.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡蓮 你該感到驕傲
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.59,0:10:48.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是你的決定 你的選擇
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.60,0:10:52.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,選擇了我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.35,0:10:55.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不相信嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.49,0:10:59.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想相信
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.80,0:11:01.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算當奴隸也在所不惜
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.31,0:11:03.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.71,0:11:06.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 我相信的是ZERO
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.52,0:11:08.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魯路修 不是你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.66,0:11:10.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 那就好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.62,0:11:11.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.96,0:11:13.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那身打扮你想穿到幾時
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.30,0:11:18.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別看 變態
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.29,0:11:20.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有這麼對ZERO說話的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.31,0:11:22.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才是對魯路修說的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.60,0:11:23.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.67,0:11:25.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.72,0:11:27.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,布里塔尼亞來了援軍
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.59,0:11:30.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,數量好多 怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.20,0:11:32.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這贏不了的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.36,0:11:35.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發生了什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.97,0:11:41.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第4特裝 開始降落
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.58,0:11:43.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓中華聯邦見識一下
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.76,0:11:45.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,皇帝陛下之威儀
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.83,0:11:48.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我神聖布里塔尼亞帝國的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.21,0:11:50.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,YES My Lord
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.86,0:12:02.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上面也來了 這下…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.69,0:12:03.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.95,0:12:07.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡拉雷斯總督出現了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.34,0:12:09.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逃脫很困難
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.02,0:12:13.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 是我贏了
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,//---------------------------------TXTB------------------------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.84,0:12:23.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第2波突擊部隊 J層以上壓制完成
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.48,0:12:26.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑色騎士團剩下的逃脫路線只有一條
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.05,0:12:30.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但那裡有我大部隊鎮守
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.52,0:12:32.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 就差把他們趕出來了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.08,0:12:34.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,準備報導
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.08,0:12:37.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恐怖分子最適合公開處刑
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.14,0:12:40.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敵人應該確信已獲得勝利
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.02,0:12:42.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,條件逐步成熟
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.24,0:12:44.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就差你那邊的樓層了？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.14,0:12:46.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,10分鐘以內吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.68,0:12:47.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.81,0:12:49.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼就以當前配置防守到底
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.44,0:12:52.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迪哈爾特的裝置呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.16,0:12:53.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,系統正常
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.85,0:12:55.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一切都按作戰計劃
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.88,0:12:58.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡是B2 發現敵方Knightmare一架
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.30,0:13:00.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.04,0:13:01.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會 剛才還…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.37,0:13:03.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,B2 怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.73,0:13:06.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敵人解除了IFF嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.04,0:13:08.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是單獨行動
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.01,0:13:10.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ZERO 這裡是P6
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.79,0:13:12.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敵人 敵人…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.68,0:13:14.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,P6
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.75,0:13:17.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡是R5 R1被擊破
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.46,0:13:20.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟糕 這樣下去會來到這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.13,0:13:24.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ZERO 你一個人先逃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.11,0:13:28.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本來我們就是佯攻 是棄子作戰
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.73,0:13:29.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.59,0:13:30.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不對
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.29,0:13:32.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你錯了 卜部
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.13,0:13:36.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光憑棄卒保帥的念頭是贏不了布里塔尼亞的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.47,0:13:40.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卜部隊長
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.86,0:13:41.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能行嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.93,0:13:44.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 物資搬運口對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.29,0:13:44.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.92,0:13:47.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要來這層 那裡是捷徑
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.33,0:14:01.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,確認了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.88,0:14:04.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,疑似以Lancelot為藍本的量產試作機
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.34,0:14:08.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎 但現在還不到捕捉的時機
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.45,0:14:09.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,破壞掉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.20,0:14:10.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.66,0:14:12.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,消失了？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.15,0:14:14.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼在這邊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.04,0:14:17.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慢著 什麼叫消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.09,0:14:44.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,C.C. 你那邊的樓層還沒搞定嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.53,0:14:48.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慌什麼 那邊不是有卡蓮和卜部嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.36,0:14:52.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這傢伙嗎 不安定要素
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.41,0:14:56.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開什麼玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.76,0:15:00.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又不是朱雀 戰略怎能被戰術擊潰
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.04,0:15:05.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,近戰我佔優勢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.75,0:15:10.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太慢了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.38,0:15:15.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,消失了？真是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.03,0:15:16.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神速
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.88,0:15:19.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.34,0:15:23.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是物理性因素 是別的什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.99,0:15:27.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會被幹掉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.04,0:15:31.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卜部
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.77,0:15:32.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卜部先生
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.20,0:15:36.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ZERO 你的真身是不是學生都無所謂
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.03,0:15:41.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「光憑棄卒保帥」那句話 我就當真了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.99,0:15:42.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紅月
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.12,0:15:43.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.13,0:15:45.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ZERO拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.60,0:15:47.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有他是最後的希望
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.03,0:15:50.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉了 拉克夏塔
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.09,0:15:52.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ZERO啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.36,0:15:57.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,日本大眾 就交給你了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.40,0:16:01.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所謂四聖劍 絕非浪得虛名
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.09,0:16:04.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卜部
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.23,0:16:12.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又是瞬間移動嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.06,0:16:14.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慢著
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.02,0:16:16.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也必須下定決心
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.56,0:16:17.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了ZERO
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.06,0:16:21.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遺憾的消息 準備就緒
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.07,0:16:22.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.38,0:16:25.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卜部 你所爭取來的這一瞬間
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.82,0:16:27.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕無白費
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.04,0:16:36.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恐怖分子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.21,0:16:37.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到會自決
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.00,0:16:39.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒文化的猴子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.41,0:16:40.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24}全機失蹤
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.15,0:16:41.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24}全機通信斷絕
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.24,0:16:42.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.91,0:16:45.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24}…識別 變更為異常等級C
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.28,0:16:48.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24}從截斷處上升到1500後 開始迴旋
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.70,0:17:01.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是了 這樣就能把空中的敵人打下地面
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.03,0:17:03.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不止如此
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.82,0:17:09.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.69,0:17:12.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,錯就錯在封鎖逃脫路線
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.93,0:17:15.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為這就等於告知了你的所在嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.62,0:17:24.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,永別了 卡拉雷斯總督
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.92,0:17:27.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總督被打敗了？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.79,0:17:29.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,康威爾卿在哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.41,0:17:30.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和總督一起…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.64,0:17:32.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那指揮系統呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.25,0:17:34.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說交給…內務省的文官？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.24,0:17:36.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慌張什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.08,0:17:40.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我來指揮
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.75,0:17:44.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這不是奪權 只是臨時措施
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.82,0:17:46.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以吾公主殿下之名起誓
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.14,0:17:48.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望你們能合作
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.10,0:17:50.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公主殿下？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.56,0:17:52.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是說科奈莉婭公主殿下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.94,0:17:53.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.72,0:17:54.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.61,0:17:57.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,YES My Lord
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.59,0:17:58.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝 感謝你們
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.50,0:18:01.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 我這就前往現場
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.74,0:18:02.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,指揮救援
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.44,0:18:04.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿爾弗雷德負責指揮警察
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.99,0:18:06.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巴特留在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.39,0:18:09.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.77,0:18:10.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.21,0:18:14.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是ZERO
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.27,0:18:18.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.53,0:18:19.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是ZERO吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.34,0:18:20.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是死了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.80,0:18:22.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但怎麼會突然…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.44,0:18:24.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會是真人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.59,0:18:27.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,日本人啊 我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.31,0:18:29.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,停止播放
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.28,0:18:31.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 不接受信號
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.52,0:18:34.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我設置的Line Omega
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.92,0:18:36.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道這個的只有…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.36,0:18:38.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ZERO
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.08,0:18:41.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你果然還活著
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.11,0:18:43.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽著 布里塔尼亞
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.83,0:18:44.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刮目相看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.41,0:18:47.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一切擁有力量的人們啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.43,0:18:50.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很悲傷
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.28,0:18:52.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戰爭與歧視
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.21,0:18:55.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,強者炫耀著惡意
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.06,0:18:59.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,維持錯誤不斷流傳的悲喜劇
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.91,0:19:03.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世界沒有任何改變
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.43,0:19:07.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我不得不復活
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.80,0:19:11.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要強者還在繼續凌虐弱者
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.28,0:19:13.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就會持續抗爭下去
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.61,0:19:16.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首先對愚蠢的卡拉雷斯總督
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.45,0:19:18.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就在剛才 已施以天誅
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.68,0:19:22.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀呀 動作還挺快嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.40,0:19:24.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,11區人的國王陛下
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.05,0:19:25.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧 朱雀
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.36,0:19:30.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,查明了 發信源是中華聯邦總領事館
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.90,0:19:32.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中華聯邦的？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.15,0:19:33.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莫非亡命過去了？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.59,0:19:35.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎樣突破包圍網的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.54,0:19:37.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.63,0:19:40.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們從倒塌的大樓裡面
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.53,0:19:42.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以巴別塔作為道路
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.36,0:19:45.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 中華聯邦是？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.83,0:19:49.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事先就說好了？不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.39,0:19:51.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是死了嗎 ZERO
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.02,0:19:52.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.77,0:19:54.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那這是冒牌貨？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.46,0:19:57.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論如何 只要突入總領事館…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.80,0:19:59.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是重大的違規行為
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.76,0:20:01.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會引起國際問題的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.46,0:20:04.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然自稱是ZERO 就是殺害皇族的罪人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.67,0:20:07.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然和EU作戰也很重要
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.63,0:20:10.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正都是無底洞
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.94,0:20:14.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,殺害總督和確保逃脫路線
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.12,0:20:15.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然同時實現
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.25,0:20:19.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種智慧和膽量
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.53,0:20:22.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是ZERO本人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.58,0:20:24.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.30,0:20:28.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,與行使錯誤力量的所有人作戰
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.83,0:20:33.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因此 我在此
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.65,0:20:37.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再次宣佈 成立日本合眾國
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.54,0:20:39.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.12,0:20:42.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都沒有聖上的敕令
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.32,0:20:45.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你對我的決定有不滿嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.45,0:20:47.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.67,0:20:51.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ZERO啊 只要是為了你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.75,0:20:53.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,合眾國…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.31,0:20:54.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,日本
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.43,0:20:56.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恐怖分子建國？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.89,0:20:58.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從這一瞬間開始
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.17,0:21:01.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個房間就是日本合眾國第一塊領土
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.77,0:21:05.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有一個房間的國家
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.89,0:21:08.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他還是那麼有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.37,0:21:11.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不問人種 主義 宗教
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.46,0:21:13.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成為國民的資格只有一條
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.86,0:21:15.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是行使正義
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.87,0:21:22.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡開始是我中華聯邦的領土
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.64,0:21:24.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.83,0:21:27.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,日後外交場上見
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.84,0:21:31.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ZERO…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.84,0:21:33.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他到底有多少利用價值
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.81,0:21:40.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若是布里塔尼亞軍 已經請回了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.02,0:21:43.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或者你是ZERO的同伴？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.35,0:21:48.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個嘛 是哪邊呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.55,0:21:51.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我對猜謎沒興趣
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.34,0:21:54.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.15,0:21:57.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是想知道真相
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.04,0:21:58.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.66,0:22:02.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我來取ZERO的性命了
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,//---------------------------------NEXT------------------------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.49,0:23:41.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,坐等無法改變世界
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.15,0:23:45.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了找到並保護娜娜莉 我需要力量
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.38,0:23:48.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比皇帝比朱雀都強的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.29,0:23:50.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一定會獲得的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.97,0:23:52.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,操縱Geass的結果
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.24,0:23:55.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必能創造出以日本合眾國為中心
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.43,0:23:57.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超越布里塔尼亞的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.09,0:24:00.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為此首先要將他
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.24,0:24:03.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將那虛偽的弟弟 羅洛…


